articles.author: Timothy Nerozzi
articles.title: Kamala Harris issues dire climate change warning in Africa: 'Existential threat to the entire planet' - Fox News
articles.description: Vice President Kamala Harris gave a dire warning about climate change during a meeting with Zambian farmers Saturday, calling it an 'existential threat to the entire planet.'
articles.content:
Vice President Kamala Harris gave a stern warning about the "existential threat" of climate change while speaking with farmers in Africa.
